      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-16">
        <div class="bg-primary-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary-700">
          <div class="text-secondary-400 mb-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Financial Analysis</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Data-Driven Insights</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary-200">Transform complex financial data into actionable intelligence for your executive team.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-primary-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary-700">
          <div class="text-secondary-400 mb-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Strategic Planning</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Future-Proof Decisions</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary-200">Develop robust financial strategies aligned with your organization's long-term vision.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-primary-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary-700">
          <div class="text-secondary-400 mb-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Risk Management</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Mitigate Uncertainty</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary-200">Identify and address financial risks before they impact your bottom line.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
